       (22,DEFAULT,'Milk Shake',DEFAULT, 'OPTIFAST® VLCD™ Shake Chocolate Sachet 53g (Pack of 18) is part of a nutritionally complete, very low calorie diet program, which contains all of the nutrients required for safe and effective weight loss, including protein to help you preserve lean muscle mass while you lose fat stores. This great tasting Chocolate Shake is a satisfying, convenient and easy to prepare product that can be enjoyed for breakfast, lunch or dinner.'),
       (22,DEFAULT,'Super Hydrating Shower',DEFAULT, 'Your skin will transform with this advanced, multipurpose 3 in 1 daily cleansing treatment oil. The soft lather gently cleanses whilst the Lanolin-Hydro Technology rebalances moisture levels long after you shower. Excellent in assisting to relieve skin irritation to protect and repair delivering instantly soft, smooth and supple skin. Enjoy soft velvety skin that hydrates continuously for 24 hours and wear your skin with pride.'),
       (22,DEFAULT,'Quick Loss Meal',DEFAULT, 'Dr Cabot is very aware of all the reasons that make it difficult for people to control their weight in modern society.These reasons include - * The abundance of fast foods high in unhealthy fats and sugar that tempt us  * The lack of time to prepare healthy meals * The lack of motivation many people feel when weight loss is too slow * The high levels of stress caused by lack of time to take care of ourselves due to the demands of family and work * Lack of support and ongoing professional advice * The fact that healthy slimming food can be more expensive than fast food and junk food'),
       (22,DEFAULT,'Hand Sanitiser Spray',DEFAULT, 'Purified Water, Alcohol (Derived from Sugar Cane), Tocopherol (Natural Vitamin E), Vegetable Glycerin, Certified Organic Jojoba Oil, Panthenol (Pro Vitamin B5), Polysorbate 20, Acrylic Polymer, Benzalkonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate, Phenoxyethanol, PHMB, Potassium Sorbate, Chloroacetamide, Tea Tree Extract, Fragrance.'),
       (23,DEFAULT,'Nicorette Cooldrops',DEFAULT, 'Whether you are trying to quit now, or want to do it in your own time, unwelcome cravings can often take over, even at times when you should be relaxed. That is why NICORETTE® Cooldrops Lozenges are here to reduce the number of cigarettes you smoke or quitting altogether. And you can use up to 15 of them a day. A higher strength 4mg lozenge is also available if you smoke more than 20 cigarettes a day.' ),
       (23,DEFAULT,'Nicabate Patches',DEFAULT, 'Whether you are a heavy or light smoker, Nicabate Patches can help you quit for good. They work by providing a continuous dose of nicotine around the clock, to protect you from the cravings whenever they strike. Giving up all your cigarettes at once is hard. With Nicabate PRE-QUIT you can continue to smoke but you will find that the urge to smoke is decreased - due to the therapeutic nicotine in Nicbate PRE-QUIT.'), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Nicorette Chewing Gumnd',DEFAULT, 'When you chew Nicorette® Classic Gum it releases controlled amounts of nicotine which are absorbed through the lining of the mouth, to help you deal with cravings and nicotine withdrawal symptoms. '), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Quitx Patches',DEFAULT, 'QuitX patches can help you stop smoking. You probably know that smoking is a very difficult habit to break. There are two sides to quitting smoking. The first is the psychological dependence on cigarettes. You have probably smoked for many years and smoking has become an important part of your life. '), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Nicotinell Patch Step Two',DEFAULT, 'Nicotinell 20 Patches 14mg X 7 are part of a carefully structured Nicotinell support program including materials designed to provide you with information to help you stop smoking (see leaflet inside carton). Nicotinell patches, being a step-down approach will reduce your nicotine dose gradually, rather than stopping suddenly. The program consists of 3 steps which you will need to follow.'), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Nicabate Minis',DEFAULT, 'Nicabate Minis 1.5mg Mint Lozenges Regular Strength X 20 act to relieve cravings in minutes. This allows you to quit one cigarette at a time, at a pace that suits you, to help you stay calm, be prepared and in control of your quit journey. Nicabate Minis® are small, fast dissolving lozenges releasing therapeutic nicotine quickly. Simply replace a few cigarettes at first, then gradually decrease the number you smoke over time. Each time you avoid reaching for a cigarette, feel proud of yourself and celebrate that little win '), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Nicabate Patches Clear',DEFAULT, 'Whether you are a heavy or light smoker, Nicabate Patches can help you quit for good. They work by providing a continuous dose of nicotine around the clock, to protect you from the cravings whenever they strike Giving up all your cigarettes at once is hard. With Nicabate PRE-QUIT you can continue to smoke but you will find that the urge to smoke is decreased - due to the therapeutic nicotine in Nicbate PRE-QUIT Nicabate PRE-QUIT combined with the Nicabate patch 10 week step down program is clinically proven to triple your chance of quitting successfully compared to cold turkey.'), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Quitx Patches M Two',DEFAULT, 'The QuitX Support Booklet contains more help for you to quit smoking, but it is not a substitute for personal counselling. Counselling is available from various groups such as Quit For Life. To get the bes out of QuitX, we encourage you to enrol in one of these groups.'), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Quitx Patches M Three',DEFAULT, 'The other side is a physical addiction to nicotine. Cigarettes contain nicotine, and your body has become dependent on nicotine. The QuitX patch delivers nicotine into your bloodstream through your skin. Using QuitX will help to gradually reduce the amount of nicotine your body craves each day. '), 
       (23,DEFAULT,'Nicotinell Gum Mint',DEFAULT, 'Nicotinell Gum 4mg Mint X 96 helps you to give up smoking by relieving the desire to smoke, as well as some of the unpleasant withdrawal effects which smokers experience when they stop smoking. Dependence on nicotine can in some cases be transferred from cigarettes to Nicotinell Gum but it is less harmful and easier to break than smoking. By giving you control over your nicotine cravings, you can effectively deal with your withdrawal symptoms as they happen.'), 
       (24,DEFAULT,'Centrum Advance',DEFAULT, 'Centrum Advance 50+ is designed to give your body the right nutrients at the right levels as you get older to help fill nutritional gaps in your diet. With the added benefit of Lutein for healthy eyes, and Lycopene for a healthy heart, Centrum Advance 50+ is complete from A to Zinc.'),
       (24,DEFAULT,'Cenovis',DEFAULT, 'Helps relieve nervousness, mild anxiety and irritability. Beneficial during times of sadness. Helps promote healthy mood balance.'),
       (24,DEFAULT,'Empty Gelatine Capsules',DEFAULT, 'Empty capsules ready to be filled with substances to be taken orally. Gelatin Capsules are capsules designed to fill any kind of medication like herbs, vitamins, and other substances. 0.95ml capacity'), 
       (24,DEFAULT,'Active Plus Fibre',DEFAULT, 'A great tasting nutritious drink, packed with a comprehensive range of essential vitamins, minerals along with the added benefit of fibre. Plus, it’s high in protein to help keep you strong and active.'),
       (24,DEFAULT,'Multivitamins Oral Liquid',DEFAULT, 'Penta-Vite® Multivitamins Oral Liquids For Infants contain 7 essential vitamins to help support healthy growth and development. Penta-vite® Multivitamins Oral Liquids For Infants may help maintain a healthy intake of vitamins in instances of fussy eating habits, appetite loss or during illness.'),
       (24,DEFAULT,'Salvital Powder',DEFAULT, 'Salvital is a saline drink that is not only thirst quenching but tastes good. It Is effervescent light lemon taste makes it a pleasant drink to have at any time of day or after playing sport.'), 
       (24,DEFAULT,'Hairy Lemon Effervescent',DEFAULT, 'HAIRY LEMON is an ideal formulation for people who feel tired due to a hectic lifestyle. It may also be of assistance to people who have trouble concentrating throughout the day. HAIRY LEMON may be used as a vitamin B formula to help relieve periods of tension and stress. Its strong recovery action also helps those recovering from a late night out.'),
       (24,DEFAULT,'Berocca Performance',DEFAULT, 'The specific combination of B group vitamins and Vitamin C in Berocca Original and Tropical help your body to release the maximum energy from the food you eat.'),
       (24,DEFAULT,'Eye Q Cap',DEFAULT, 'Eye Q is a combination of the specific omega 3 and omega 6 fatty acids required for optimal eye and brain function, delivered in the form of high grade natural oils. We do NOT  use the word natural lightly: in processing and selecting our oils, we ensure that only pure, natural form fatty acids are used. Our main reason for this specification is that many who take eye q are youngsters, and so we believe this makes it even more important that there are no synthetic or artificial elements within the formulation.'), 
       (24,DEFAULT,'Ethical Nutrients',DEFAULT, 'May help reduce the frequency and severity of outbreaks of cold sores. Nutritional support for normal/healthy immune function. Astragalus is traditionally used to maintain normal body defences and for strengthening the immune system.');
       
       

